34:36.880 --> 34:38.940
Pelaku asli Kasus Huaiguang, Qi Yan.

34:39.630 --> 34:40.360
Apakah tim satgas pernah memeriksa

34:40.360 --> 34:41.800
latar belakang keluarganya

34:41.800 --> 34:43.360
